PrecisAmendments to the ACCESS TO INFORMATION REGULATIONS which (a) provide that where the reproduction of government records is specifically restricted by a statute other than the Access to Information Act, the applicant may be granted permission to examine the original records, and (b) correct errors in the French version of section 4.

precis:
Amendments to the ACCESS TO INFORMATION REGULATIONS which (a) provide that
where the reproduction of government records is specifically restricted by
a statute other than the Access to Information Act, the applicant may be
granted permission to examine the original records, and (b) correct errors
in the French version of section 4.
